ess or\neven integrability conditions on the sample. We describe the counterpart of\nLloyd's algorithm and prove generalization bounds for these new $k$-means\ncriteria.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jan 2021 17:12:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Feb 2021 17:50:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-09"}
