$, the sets of minimal forbidden induced subgraphs are the same as those for\nthe property $\\operatorname{mr}(G,\\mathbb{F}_2)\\leq k$, and we exhibit this set\nfor $c_2(G)\\leq2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Jan 2021 15:41:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Apr 2021 20:39:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 19:32:12 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 6 Dec 2022 21:47:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-08"}
